            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Hd1e111" type="question-title">Quando loquendum sit</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>
      ¶ Quando sit loquendum. Rubrica. 3
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e116">SAlomon in prouerb. c. 15.</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e125">Responsio mol 
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>lis frangit iram sermo durus susci
        <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>tat furorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e133">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e130">18. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e135">Qui prius respon
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>det quam audiat stultum esse se demonstrat: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>confusione dignum.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e144"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e143">26 c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e146">Ne responde
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>as stulto iuxta stultitiam suam: ne efficiaris
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>ei similis. Responde stulto iuxta stultitiam
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>suam: ne sapiens esse sibi videatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e156">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e159">Aristotelis topicorum. li. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e160">Nisi planum sit
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>quod dicitur: non pigritandum est dicere et non
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>intelligere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e168"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e171">Idem elencorum. lib. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e170">Null <!--189.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="75-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>eorum que equiuoca sunt conuenit respon
        <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>dere simpliciter. In quibus est obscurum quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>ponitur non concedendum simpliciter.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e187">
               <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e194">Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e191">Si est
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>tibi intellectus responde proximo. Sinau
        <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>tem sit manus tua super os tuum: ne capia
        <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>ris in verbo indisciplinato et confundaris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e201">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e210">11. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e205">Priusquam audias ne respondeas ver
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>bum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e211"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e220">32. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e213">Si bis interrogatus fueris ha
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>beat caput responsum tuum. In multis esto
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>quasi inscius et audita tacens simul et que
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>rens.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e224"> 
             / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e235">41. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e226">Erubescite a salutaribus de
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>silentio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e232">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e247">Paulus apostolus in epistola. i. ad corin
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>thios. c. 14.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e236">Quomodo dicit amen super tuam be
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>nedictionem quicquid dicas nescitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e244">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e262">Lex dige. ti. de legibus. l. infrascripta.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e248">In
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>ciuile est nisi tota lege perspecta: vna aliqua
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>pticula eius proposita iudicare: vel respondere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e256">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e276">Marcialis cocus l. vndique suscepto. c. 3.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e260">Iratus irato animo respondet alanus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>Et se iactat in hoc grande nimis vicium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e268">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e290">Auctor l. de for. honeste vite. c. 4.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e272">Requi
        <lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>renti facile responde.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e278">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e301">Ambrosius de officiis. li. i. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e282">Noli respon
        <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>dere irato ad iracundiam eius: siue in pru
        <lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>denti ad imprudentiam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e291">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e316">Macrobius saturnaliorum: lib. 3 impro
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>hemio.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e295">Qui vult esse amenus consultor ea
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>interroget que sunt interrogato facilia re
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>sponsum: et que scit illum sedula exercitatio
        <lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>ne didicisse. Gaudet enim quisquis cum pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>uocatur ad doctrinam suam in medium pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>ferendam: quia nemo vult latere quod didicit:
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>maxime si scientia quam labore acquisiuit cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>paucis illa familiaris et plurimis sit incogni
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>ta: vt de astronomia: vel dialetica: ceterisque
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>similibus. tunc enim videtur consequi fru
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>ctum laboris cum adipiscitur occasionem
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>publicandi: que didicit sine ostentationis
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>nota. qua caret qui non ingerit: sed innita
        <lb ed="#V" n="42" break="no"/>tur vt proferat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-d1e329">
               <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Rd1e357">Prouerb. metrice extraord l vag.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d61691-Qd1e333">Sub
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>dubio forsan respondent sepe periti.
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>In respondendo nunquam celer esse memento. <!--189.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
